android.webkit.gears
Class UrlInterceptHandlerGears.ServiceResponse

java.lang.Object
  android.webkit.gears.UrlInterceptHandlerGears.ServiceResponse
Enclosing class:
UrlInterceptHandlerGears
public class UrlInterceptHandlerGears.ServiceResponse
extends Object

Object returned by the native side, containing information needed to pass the entire response back to the browser or HttpRequestAndroid. Works from either an in-memory array or a file on disk.
